listing_desc.18: North Rome Farmers Market has some of the best produce in the city of Rome, Georgia. Our fruits and vegetables are grown on our own property without any chemicals. We are very excited about bringing fresh produce to our side of town. We look forward to providing a variety of tomatoes, cucumbers, squash, okra, and more.
